message.body: Hey hunter. What are they going for? Thanks
I'm not sure what it is going to come out to after getting it trucked to my house but probably around $300 for 5 shelf big unit and $200 for 5 shelf smaller unit
Good prices. I don't think I can swing it right now though. Anyway, thanks again and it'd be nice to see you sometime soon in 2014

Yeah man . We'll they will probably be sitting in my living room for a while if I don't sell them all. I'm not really drinking nowadays so I pretty much stay at home all the time. But I should have you and some people over for dinner
That'd be great man. In fact, I'm endeavoring to ride a similar wagon these days. No more time or money for the bozo w/ the bottle skit. Keep in touch
